{% extends 'base.html.twig' %}
{% block title %}
	{{ ad.title }}
{% endblock %}
{% block body %}
	<div class="add-tittle" style="background-image : url({{ad.coverImage}})">
		<div class="container">
			<h1>{{ad.title}}</h1>
			<p>{{ad.introduction}}</p>
			<p><strong>{{ad.rooms}} Chambres </strong>pour <strong>{{ad.price}}</strong> FCFA par nuits</p>
			<div class="btn btn-success left">Reservez !!!</div>
		</div>
		
	</div>
	
	<div class="container">
		<div class="row">
			<div class="col-md-8 mb-3">
				<h1>{{ad.content|raw}}</h1>
				<div id="carouselExampleIndicators" class="carousel slide" data-ride="carousel">
					<ol class="carousel-indicators">
					{% for images in ad.images %}
						<li data-target="#carouselExampleIndicators" data-slide-to="{{loop.index0}}" class="active"></li>
					{% endfor %}
					</ol>
					<div class="carousel-inner">
					{% for images in ad.images %}
						<div class="carousel-item {% if loop.first %} active  {% endif %} ">
							<img class="d-block w-100" src="{{images.url}}" alt="First slide">
						</div>
					{% endfor %}
					</div>
					<a class="carousel-control-prev" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="prev">
						<span class="carousel-control-prev-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						<span class="sr-only">Previous</span>
					</a>
					<a class="carousel-control-next" href="#carouselExampleIndicators" role="button" data-slide="next">
						<span class="carousel-control-next-icon" aria-hidden="true"></span>
						<span class="sr-only">Next</span>
					</a>
				</div>
			</div>
			<div class="col">
				<div class="row">
					<div class="col-4">
						<img src="http://placehold.it/64x64" alt="">
					</div>
					<div class="col">
						<h1>Issa TELLY</h1>
						<span class="badge badge-primary">3 annonces !</span>
					</div>
				</div>
				<p>Lorem ipsum dolor sit amet, consectetur adipisicing elit. Saepe earum magni illum sint ducimus omnis iure. Consequuntur possimus, dolorum quae!</p>
				<p>Nulla sunt atque quibusdam repudiandae voluptatem. Molestias officia cupiditate, maxime pariatur qui eligendi aliquid, ut accusantium iusto, harum rem repellendus!</p>
				<p>Odit rerum a ad autem laborum mollitia cum perspiciatis esse recusandae quas tempora incidunt ea facilis corporis ipsum, soluta beatae.</p>
			</div>
		</div>
	</div>
	
{% endblock %}